OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FA dry day for many with sunny
OL,6,Fspells, though the cloud may be thick
OL,7,Fenough to give the odd light shower
OL,8,Ffrom time to time. Feeling a little
OL,9,Ffresher.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FA
OL,12,Ffine day on Wednesday, with sunny
OL,13,Fspells. Most likely dry on Thursday,
OL,14,Fbut rain possible by the evening. This
OL,15,Fclearing to leave another dry and
OL,16,Fsunny day on Friday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
